resources.name: Detailed information on public opinion website

description:
DG MARKT has commissioned a Special Survey on this subject in the 10 New European Union Member States.
The interviews were carried out between 3 January and 15 February 2005 as part of the Eurobarometer 63.1.
This report will focus on 8 services of general interest:
- Electricity
- Natural gas
- Fixed telephony
- Mobile telephony
- Postal services for regular mail such as letters, postcards or packages
- Local transport (Trams, Buses, Metro...)
- Rail transport
- Air transport

#####The results by volumes are distributed as follows:
* Volume A: Countries
* Volume AA: Groups of countries
* Volume A' (AP): Trends
* Volume AA' (AAP): Trends of groups of countries
* Volume B: EU/socio-demographics
* Volume C: Country/socio-demographics
title: Special Eurobarometer 226: Price and quality of services of general interest
name: S500_63_1_EBS226
alternative_title: Price and quality of services of general interest
